{"tid":1560723,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［我是藍絲，我撐警察］食肆表態行動","createTime":"2019-09-11T10:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T15:25:39.000Z","uid":186989,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"51bbb480215bfb20f8ce15429d7718ad0909a134","tid":1560723,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:22:50.000Z","msg":"黃屍頻頻發表針對警察的言論，尤其部分從事飲食業暴徒，聲稱會在警察的餐飲內「加料」，白汁、凍撚茶等，令人毛骨悚然！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了令阿sir madam食得放心，本人呼籲各個撐警食店，參與「［我是藍絲，我撐警察］食肆表態行動」，張貼「我撐警察」之貼紙在門口/收銀機等當眼處。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呼籲各位高手製作宣傳貼紙設計圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e08bd077068f965b0b96b9723f20ee627115bf","tid":1560723,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:23:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"028c8526dfb8d42bb2e79ee2ad6b0db2d181ab24","tid":1560723,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 